section.section:
"Service contract" does not include:
A guaranty;
A maintenance agreement that does not include a provision for the repair, replacement, or maintenance of a product because of an operational or structural failure due to a defect in materials, workmanship, or normal wear and tear;
A warranty, service contract, or maintenance agreement offered by a public utility on its transmission devices to the extent it is regulated by the Public Service Commission;
A mechanical repair contract under § 15-311.2 of the Transportation Article; or
Mechanical breakdown insurance.
